    "description": "Lucky you, you've been hired as a tester for Chaperon Inc., the wacky typewriter manufacturer!<br><br>Write excerpts of known texts as fast as you can to get the best times in this arcade speed-typing game!<br><br>Regular keyboards are out of the question though, Chaperon Inc. will provide you with their own typewriters, such as:<br><strong>* The <u>Binarion</u>, a simple-looking toy with only two buttons!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093090/extras/binarion_gameplay_600.PNG?t=1731778399\" /></span><br><br><strong>* <u>Morley</u> the Morse machine, beep beep!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093090/extras/morse_600.PNG?t=1731778399\" /></span><br><br><strong>* Or even the <u>Rouletter</u>, which is classified as &quot;not gambling&quot;, phew!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093090/extras/casino_gameplay_600.PNG?t=1731778399\" /></span><br><br>* And more, for a total of <strong>8 unique machines</strong> and <strong>36 texts to write</strong>!<br><br>Well... get to work, won't you?",
